<h2 id="creating-blog-posts">Creating Blog Posts</h2>

<p>Blog posts go in the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_posts/</code> directory with the naming convention: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">YYYY-MM-DD-title.md</code></p>

<div class="language-yaml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nn">---</span>
<span class="na">layout</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">post</span>
<span class="na">title</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">Your</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">Post</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">Title"</span>
<span class="na">date</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">2025-08-30</span>
<span class="na">author</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">Your</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">Name"</span>
<span class="na">excerpt</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s2">"</span><span class="s">Brief</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">description</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">for</span><span class="nv"> </span><span class="s">previews"</span>
<span class="na">reading_time</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="m">5</span>  <span class="c1"># Optional: estimated reading time in minutes</span>
<span class="nn">---</span>

<span class="s">Your post content here using Markdown syntax.</span>

<span class="c1">## Math Support</span>
<span class="na">The template includes MathJax for mathematical expressions</span><span class="pi">:</span>

<span class="na">Inline math</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">$E = mc^2$</span>

<span class="na">Display math</span><span class="pi">:</span>
